name: Physician workforce assessment fee; license; physician workforce information
text:
Note
 
  Repeal of section on June 30, 2017, by L Sp 2009, c 18, §9; L 2012, c 186, §3(2) deleted by L 2017, c 40, §2.
  Disbursements to special fund.  L Sp 2009, c 18, §4; L 2012, c 186, §3(2); L 2017, c 40, §2.
  Physician workforce assessment report to legislature beginning in 2011 and every year thereafter.  L Sp 2009, c 18, §5; L 2012, c 186, §3(1).
